Title: Local well-posedness of nonlinear dispersive equations on modulation
  spaces
Authors: \'Arp\'ad B\'enyi, Kasso A. Okoudjou
Categories: math.AP math.CA
Comments: 11 pages
MSC-class: 35Q55 (Primary), 35C15, 42B15, 42B35 (Secondary)
\\
  By using tools of time-frequency analysis, we obtain some improved local
well-posedness results for the NLS, NLW and NLKG equations with Cauchy data in
modulation spaces $M{p, 1}_{0,s}$.
